name: poc_grain_sack
desc: First attempt at Canopy POC building grain
author: adahl

memberSetCode.code: SELECT fact_id FROM s_fact WHERE fact_id <= 9 ORDER BY 1;

SELECT d2_id, goofy_d2_id FROM ( SELECT 1 AS oid, gr204_oid, goofy_d2_id AS d2_id, d2_id AS goofy_d2_id FROM grain_204 WHERE d2_id NOT IN (1) AND goofy_d2_id NOT IN (SELECT d2_id FROM dim_2 WHERE d2_name IN ('automotive')) UNION SELECT 2 AS oid, gr204_oid, goofy_d2_id AS d2_id, goofy_d2_id FROM grain_204 WHERE d2_id = 1 AND goofy_d2_id NOT IN (SELECT d2_id FROM dim_2 WHERE d2_name IN ('automotive')) ) a ORDER BY oid, gr204_oid;
SELECT goofy_d4_id AS d4_id, d4_id AS goofy_d4_id FROM grain_404 WHERE d4_id = (SELECT d4_id FROM dim_4 WHERE d4_name = 'assigned') ORDER BY gr404_oid;

SELECT d5_id, type_id FROM ( SELECT * FROM ( WITH s_type AS (SELECT type_id FROM s_type WHERE type_group = 'product_reporting' AND type_name = 'summary') SELECT row_number() over() AS ord, type_id, d5_id, d5_name FROM s_type,( SELECT 0 AS o1, row_number() over() AS o2, d5_id, d5_name FROM (SELECT * FROM dim_5 WHERE d5_product_reporting ~* 'summary' AND d5_name NOT IN ('rv-ep','49300','chgcf','30001','endfb') ORDER BY d5h18_oid) a UNION SELECT 1 AS o1, row_number() over() AS o2, d5_id, d5_name FROM (SELECT * FROM dim_5 WHERE d5_product_reporting ~* 'summary' AND d5_name IN ('rv-ep','49300','chgcf','30001','endfb') ORDER BY d5h18_oid DESC) b ORDER BY o1,o2 ) a ORDER BY o1,o2 ) a UNION SELECT row_number() over() AS ord, * FROM ( WITH s_type AS (SELECT type_id FROM s_type WHERE type_group = 'product_reporting' AND type_name = 'all') SELECT type_id, d5_id, d5_name FROM s_type,dim_5 WHERE d5_product_reporting ~* 'all' ORDER BY d5_id ) a UNION SELECT row_number() over() AS ord, * FROM ( WITH s_type AS (SELECT type_id FROM s_type WHERE type_group = 'product_reporting' AND type_name = 'detail') SELECT type_id, d5_id, d5_name FROM s_type,dim_5 WHERE d5_product_reporting ~* 'detail' ORDER BY d5_id ) a UNION SELECT row_number() over() AS ord, * FROM ( WITH s_type AS (SELECT type_id FROM s_type WHERE type_group = 'product_reporting' AND type_name = 'clinops') SELECT type_id, d5_id, d5_name FROM s_type,dim_5 WHERE d5_product_reporting ~* 'clinops' ORDER BY d5_id ) a  ORDER BY type_id, ord ) a;

SELECT grain_505.goofy_d5_id AS d5_id, d5_id AS goofy_d5_id  FROM grain_510 JOIN grain_505 USING (d5_ID) WHERE grain_510.goofy_d5_id = (SELECT type_id FROM s_type WHERE type_name = 'summary' AND type_group = 'product_reporting')  ORDER BY gr510_oid;
SELECT goofy_d6_id AS d6_id, d6_id AS goofy_d6_id FROM grain_605 WHERE d6_id IN (SELECT d6_id FROM dim_6 WHERE d6_name IN ('level_1_2_node','level_2_83307_node','level_2_3_node')) ORDER BY gr605_oid;
